---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Story | Rubadue Wire"
  description="Since 1977, Rubadue Wire has been pioneering wire solutions with cutting-edge technology, specializing in triple-insulated wire and Litz wire. As a 100% employee-owned company, we solve wire and cable challenges when high performance and reliability are critical."
  category="About"
  eyebrow="About"
  headerTitle="Our Story"
>
  <div class="py-8 sm:py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      {/* Description Section */}
      <div class="mx-auto lg:mx-0">
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg/8">
          We solve wire and cable challenges when high performance and
          reliability are critical. As a 100% employee-owned company, we are
          committed to innovation, quality, and exceptional customer service.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Mission & Vision Section */}
      <div class="mt-12 mb-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div
            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-primary/20 bg-card text-card-foreground shadow"
          >
            <div
              class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/40 via-primary to-primary/40"
            >
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3
                class="flex items-center gap-2 text-2xl font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight mb-6"
              >
                <Target className="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
                Our Mission
              </h3>
              <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
                We solve wire and cable challenges when high performance and
                reliability are critical.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-primary/20 bg-card text-card-foreground shadow"
          >
            <div
              class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/40 via-primary to-primary/40"
            >
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3
                class="flex items-center gap-2 text-2xl font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight mb-6"
              >
                <Eye className="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
                Our Vision
              </h3>
              <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
                Create the premier brand in developing and manufacturing
                specialty wire and cable to support tomorrow's innovation.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="my-12 border-t border-primary/10" />

      {/* History Timeline Section */}
      <div>
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 mb-10 sm:mb-16">
          <h2
            class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground"
          >
            Our History
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 sm:mt-6 text-base sm:text-lg/8 text-muted-foreground">
            Since 1977, we've been pioneering innovations in wire manufacturing,
            consistently expanding our capabilities and reach to better serve
            our customers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <Timeline client:visible data={timelineEvents} />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
